{"tid":657882,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"26場入0球！高普掃走「神鋒」粉絲讚英明","createTime":"2018-05-08T13:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T17:24:54.000Z","uid":1426,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e2dc9f2b279827b274cd6ed84a6ab7154a16893d","tid":657882,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180508/photo/bkn-20180508153030903-0508_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180508153351\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180508%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180508153030903-0508_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180508153351&h=2fe54251&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n利物浦今季入波入到停唔到，「埃及文明」個個喺高普手上都士哥大爆發，不過「紅軍」原來都有前鋒係唔識入波，上年拎咗世青盃MVP嘅蘇蘭基，今季為利物浦各項賽事上陣26場，入波數未竟然係「0」，所以近日有傳格拉斯哥流浪新帥謝拉特想借用蘇蘭基，一眾利物浦球迷即刻叫好，網民@C_LordtheGreen話：「唔理蘇蘭基有幾後生，總之呢一刻佢弱到爆，唔好畀佢再接近利物浦一隊。」@SmithyVegas更抵死表示：「仲裁法庭判咗利物浦要畀幾多培養費車路士未？依家蘇蘭基咁嘅表現，係咪可以回水？」"},{"pid":"6605cbb9c5f54aa1820de5b2736df81b3b3ad3fb","tid":657882,"uid":64464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34542d37b7e9c3003e6abd234e35d02262a1555a","tid":657882,"uid":2033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"永遠的零<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  @A09😍"},{"pid":"040150283f2736337c6a74e7b41042462b7c11ee","tid":657882,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34542d37b7e9c3003e6abd234e35d02262a1555a","tid":657882,"uid":2033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"永遠的零<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  @A09😍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:06:20.000Z","msg":"咪jer"},{"pid":"1e04479b71923636c4a9ca522a6a642df0601613","tid":657882,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:06:48.000Z","msg":